<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bills - Democratic Tap On</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-pzjw8f+ua7Kw1TIqQuFFntxg3MhZl8VV7RqIql9WLYBOrl53EBr3sF5HKvonQdcJ" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
</head>
<body style="background-color: #000; color: #fff;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mt-5">
            <h1 class="font-weight-bold">ALL BILLS BEFORE THE HOUSE</h1>
            <p class="lead">These bills will be debated when the government permits</p>
            <h2>HOW DO YOU WANT OUR REP TO VOTE?</h2>
            <div class="search-bar mt-4 mb-4">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Keywords" style="display: inline-block; width: auto; margin-right: 10px;">
                <button class="btn btn-primary">Filter Options</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Stop pork barrelling</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">This bill aims to inform the governance of the use of public resources to ensure fairness and transparency in the allocation of funds.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Assisted Suicide Communications</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">The bill addresses the penalties for suicide-related material, including assisting or enabling suicide through communication channels.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Fair Elections</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">This bill aims to improve transparency, reduce financial influence, and level the playing field in political campaigning and elections.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">STOP IMPORTING ILLEGAL LOGGING</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">The measures proposed aim to support the restrictions on illegal logging and importation.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">STOP OFFSHORE OIL EXPLORATION</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">This bill aims to ensure safer energy practices and reduce offshore oil explorations that endanger the environment.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Vaping Safety</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">This bill seeks to impose transparency, reduce harmful additives, and improve safety regulations for vaping products.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Read More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>



    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jquery@3.6.0/dist/jquery.min.js" integrity="sha384-KyZXEAg3QhqLMpG8r+Knujsl5/0U7Bv7U4jCf5Sd2z1qq5L5r5Mvv4lRJ6bE/r4+" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-LtrjvnR4Twt/qOuYxC/8fhkMvYhVOcI3B5Z4swO7pS6XbzFqZqkWzc3EsQdT9MjF" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <footer class="footer mt-auto py-3 bg-dark text-white">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <span>&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year - Democratic Tap On. All rights reserved.</span>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
